Words appear: "Extravagant Inventions. The Princely Furniture of the Roentgens."
"Berlin Secretary Cabinet"

2
00:00:06.150 --> 00:00:16.980 line:-1%
Crowned with a dome with a chiming clock, the tall, ornate cabinet features intricate marquetry panels - veneers inset with wood and ivory, and embellished with copper, to form patterns and images.

3
00:00:17.150 --> 00:00:35.790 line:-1%
Keys unlock panels that depict various scenes - such as a man painting at an easel and a small gathering of musicians.  The panels swing open, revealing hidden drawers. One small panel slides over to offer access to a keyhole. Drawers pop open and swivel to one side.

4
00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:42.010 line:-1%
A large panel lowers to form a writing desk with a pattern of concentric circles.

5
00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:54.490 line:-1%
Words appear:  "Theatrical players conceal hidden compartments."  A panel showing an actor peeking out from behind a curtain slides to one side.  Another slides in - a man leaning on a cane.

6
00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:01.870 line:-1%
An attendant presses a decorative button and a drawer springs out.  "Inkwell and sand sifter used for writing" are inside.

7
00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:05.900 line:-1%
More buttons activate more drawers and panels.

8
00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:18.760 line:-1%
A look inside the cabinet shows weights and pulleys.  "An internal mechanism reveals hidden drawers."  Gleaming metal decorations incorporate the buttons into the design.

9
00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:31.000 line:-1%
A hidden strong box pops up to the level of the writing desk.  A key unlocks the rectangular wooden box and its two small drawers.

10
00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:40.900 line:-1%
In the section above the writing desk, a key turned to the left and to the right causes twin panels to swivel open.

11
00:01:42.150 --> 00:01:48.680 line:-1%
A striped covering pushes back to reveal a deep drawer.

12
00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:55.670 line:-1%
An attendant unlocks the larger panel between the twins.

13
00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:13.980 line:-1%
The attendant turns a key.  More words:  "An internal mechanism releases the hidden easel."  A cord over a pulley raises a weight.  At the front of the cabinet, polished wooden panels unfold, creating an easel.  The attendant demonstrates the hidden easel one more time.

